{"tid":407770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成條魚生咁食,係咪好食d?(二)","createTime":"2017-09-20T16:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T17:19:06.000Z","uid":72915,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f19e75ae211dc05769cb6a4ff797b9e06ded817c","tid":407770,"uid":72915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"話說,小弟上次開左個食希靈魚post,反應幾熱烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/399144/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/399144/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n有巴絲留言,就話不如試食下三文魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁今日就一於試下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/001913_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F001913_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=082f366a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為上次希靈魚食唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今日整1/4條出黎試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/002247_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F002247_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b49f0b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次有巴絲話都試過成條食,點大量醬油會更好味咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日一於證實下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n結果<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/002524_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F002524_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=29ab6cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來真係幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三文魚成條食都唔會太膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但d筋位真係幾難咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食到好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/002727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F002727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=44c536f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最終緊係食哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a67cc6407b62b691b139cccd83b8d8b4b1cf45","tid":407770,"uid":37182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"幾錢邊度買？"},{"pid":"aa6841eefa3f7ba690a574fbebd16548963e8d25","tid":407770,"uid":23247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201